research_municipality_step.notes: Newark, NJ operates under a Mayor-Council Plan C form of government. The Mayor is Ras J. Baraka. The Municipal Council consists of nine members: four at-large and five representing specific wards. Information on council members is based on sources current as of November 2025 and official city listings. There was a minor discrepancy in older sources regarding the Council President and Central Ward representative, but the most recent information from Wikipedia and the official Newark website has been prioritized.
